{
  "stem": "24268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I think everybody tried to look up to, and to be like them, like parents with their-- that's what in their pride, I think, that which every parents, I assume, is the same way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our cousins-- like I say, we've been together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'd play together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we see each other in time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a-- we had also communicate together-- how do you say-- with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of them been our age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was easy to communicate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had our friends, which they-- we'd like to be with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what else can I say?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When did things start to change in Sosnowiec?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just like I say, just before the war, when it start to get very tense-- the situation-- and my mom-- just shortly before the war, they were talking-- they tried to cover from us-- is it  time to change?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tried to whisper-- they whispered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want the children to know everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So naturally, I wasn't informed about anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Grandpa-- Daddy always read [INAUDIBLE] the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, they'd send us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent me and my sister, and their aunts, and their younger two boys and girls to my uncle, to [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Slawkow ?], where my mom came from, to my uncle-- try to avoid from anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they heard the Germans, the war, was coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And day it can break out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sent us out there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed with the uncle, with my grandma and the whole family, with their children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how we remained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents remained with my brother in Sosnowiec, in hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went into some distant relatives, which they also had grown up boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they thought, for time being, they are safe.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
